def find_maximum_star_values(test_cases):
    results = []
    for case in test_cases:
        (N, arr) = case
        a = [0] / (max(arr) + 1)
        star_val = []
        for i in range(len(arr)):
            j = 1
            val = 0
            while j * arr[i] <= len(a):
                val += a[j * arr[i] - 1]
                j += 1
            star_val.append(val)
            a[arr[i] - 1] += 1
        results.append(max(star_val))
    return results
